data.description: RARE OPPORTUNITY! ~2 acres across the street from Samsung development! This lot has frontage on 3 sides with almost 600' of frontage on County Road 404. Taylor is on the verge of becoming the next boom town with incredible residential and commercial projects in the works. The property is not in a floodplain and has access to Jonah Water, Electric, and currently on septic. Located outside city limits and in the Taylor ETJ. (Ask agent on usage/restrictions as we are in talks with the city)
